o What You Need:
  --------------
  (You will need a blank disk-with a label saying CAPTIVE FREEDOM DISK.
  This will be used to save your progress during your quest)

o How to Load Captive - The Quest for Freedom
  -------------------------------------------
  To avoid any risk of infection of this disk by virus,
  keep the write-protect tab on your game disk open.

  Insert the Captive Disk into the disk drive and turn on the computer.
  The game will load automatically.
  Read the Instruction manual completely in order to get the most out of
  CAPTIVE - THE QUEST FOR FREEDOM.

